  background-color: rgb(255, 99, 71); /* Tomato */
}

span {
  color: rgb(0, 128, 0); /* Green */
}
```

> **Note:** Values range from 0 to 255.

---

## 4. **HSL (Hue, Saturation, Lightness)**
- More intuitive way to represent colors.
