let weather = (temperature > 25) ? 'Hot' : 'Cool';
console.log(weather);
```

> **Expected Output:**
> Hot

---

## 7. Summary

| Component               | Description                         |
|------------------------|-------------------------------------|
| `condition`             | The test expression                 |
| `expressionIfTrue`      | Result if condition is true         |
| `expressionIfFalse`     | Result if condition is false        |

